"126B":{"department":"EDUC","number":"126B","title":"Public Service Leadership Program Practicum","description":"This course is for students in the Public Service Leadership Program offered through the Haas Center for Public Service. Designed as a follow-up course to EDUC 126A: Introduction to Public Service Leadership, the PSLP Practicum provides an opportunity for PSLP students to reflect on their own leadership experiences and to learn from each other&#39;s leadership experiences while continuing to build a community of peer service leaders. The PSLP Practicum will meet every other week throughout the quarter.","min_units":1,"max_units":1,"gers":[""],"primary":[[{"instructors":[],"meeting-times":[{"days":[false,true,false,false,false],"start":"16:15:00","end":"18:05:00"}]}],[],[{"instructors":[],"meeting-times":[{"days":[false,true,false,false,false],"start":"16:15:00","end":"18:05:00"}]}]]},
"130":{"department":"EDUC","number":"130","title":"Introduction to Counseling (PSYCH 148)","description":"The goal of counseling is to help others to create more satisfying lives for themselves.  Clients learn to create and capitalize on unexpected events to open up new opportunities.  The success of counseling is judged, not by the words and actions of the counselor, but by the progress that the client makes in the real world after counseling itself is ended.  Students are encouraged to exert their full efforts within reasonable time limits to improve their competence.","min_units":3,"max_units":3,"gers":[""],"primary":[[],[{"instructors":[],"meeting-times":[{"days":[true,false,false,false,false],"start":"15:15:00","end":"17:05:00"}]}],[]]},
"131":{"department":"EDUC","number":"131","title":"Mediation for Dispute Resolution (PSYCH 152)","description":"Mediation as more effective and less expensive than other forms of settling disputes such as violence, lawsuits, or arbitration. How mediation can be structured to maximize the chances for success. Simulated mediation sessions.","min_units":3,"max_units":3,"gers":[""],"primary":[[{"instructors":[],"meeting-times":[{"days":[true,false,false,false,false],"start":"15:15:00","end":"17:05:00"}]}],[],[{"instructors":[],"meeting-times":[{"days":[true,false,false,false,false],"start":"15:15:00","end":"17:05:00"}]}]]},
